stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> ListingDetail
  ListingDetail --> LoginRequired: anonymous
  ListingDetail --> VerifyEmail: unverified email
  ListingDetail --> OwnerEdit: owner
  ListingDetail --> ContactDisabled: unavailable / moderation / migration
  ListingDetail --> ContactReady: can contact
  ListingDetail --> PaywallRequired: unlock required
  ContactReady --> StartingConversation: click contact
  StartingConversation --> MessageThread: success
  StartingConversation --> StartError: auth / rate / block / listing / paywall error
  StartError --> ContactReady: toast shown / loading reset / retry
  StartError --> LoginRequired: unauthorized / session expired
  StartError --> PaywallRequired: paywall required
  PaywallRequired --> CheckoutOpening: select offer
  CheckoutOpening --> CheckoutReturn: Stripe return
  CheckoutReturn --> ContactReady: fulfilled
  CheckoutReturn --> PaywallRequired: canceled / failed / timeout
  MessageThread --> Sending: submit message
  Sending --> MessageThread: persisted
  Sending --> SendError: rate / auth / block / listing / network
  MessageThread --> Blocked: block relation
  Blocked --> MessageThread: unblock
  MessageThread --> Polling: realtime unavailable
  Polling --> MessageThread: new messages
